											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="AnimationTags" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[PN] Shaowheart’s Dad (now in elf form). On the ground, clearly just been hit by the Sharran’s, reaching up towards Shadowheart, desperate, his mouth moves as if he’s crying something out (won’t be heard), Masked Sharrans - one moving back having just struck the elf, the others pointing their weapons at him, calm and in control, but aggressive, A masked Sharaan steps forward, reaches up in a big anticipation for a strike, brings their arm down fast and hard, " />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
