										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Young SH's POV: the wolf has transformed into an elf man. On the ground, wounded and surrounded by masked, cloaked figures. He reaches out towards the child desperately, crying out something unheard. A masked figure steps forward, back to camera and arm raised. They strike the elf (blow unseen)." />
										</node>
